      "message": "Hmm, I\u0027m not sure that would not end up polluting temp dir with maybe 1e5 android-user-guid dirs, and deleting them all would still be the same amount of work.\n\nI\u0027m also exploring solutions beyond this:\n\na. figure out how to get liveness without issuing adb commands (ideally)\nb. run adb commands in a way that does not require file creation\n\nI will go with this suboptimal solution for now until we go with one of those; wouldn\u0027t it be great to not have to do file creation per second?",
